snippet.title: Falcon Beertender 2 E-Game (Windows game 200?)
snippet.description:
Falcon Beertender 2 is a simple Swedish game by E-Game.
It's a sequel (follow-up) to 1.
The main player has to give a glass of beer to a customer and receive the empty glass.
You make them go to the left of the game screen absolutely.
